{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_UnSetShootable}}
'''A_UnSetShootable'''

(no parameters)


Makes the calling actor unshootable by clearing its {{flag|SHOOTABLE}} flag and giving it the {{Flag|NONSHOOTABLE}} flag instead. An unshootable actor can no longer be hit by hitscan weapons and is unaffected by missiles and explosions.

